{"about_the_game":"By extremely popular demand, we are pleased to release our third collection of vanity items for Grim Dawn. The items included are themed around several of Grim Dawn\u2019s enigmatic deities. Whether you are an old fan or picking up the game for the first time, you can be sure to find an exceptional new look to conquer Cairn in style.<br><br>The items in this DLC can be applied to existing gear to transform the look while retaining the original stats. They do not provide any gameplay stats or bonuses on their own.<br><br>Tear your foes apart and sow terror on the battlefield by embodying the visage of the very gods!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701090/extras/DLC_Loyalist03_Chthon01_In-Game02.gif?t=1709053495\" /><br><br><u>Loyalist Item Pack 3 items can be claimed in-game from the NPC &quot;Lancel the Knight&quot; who stands outside the gates of Devil's Crossing, by selecting the \u201cI wish to tap into the divine\u201d dialogue option.</u><br><br><strong>Note that this illusion pack requires version v1.2.0.4 or higher. For owners of the Ashes of Malmouth DLC, the items you receive from Lancel are added to your Illusionist collection rather than being applied directly to items.</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>armor of the greatest among the gods, Empyrion<br></li><li>vestments of the keeper of the veil, Rattosh<br></li><li>chains of the dying god, Ch'thon<br></li><li>vestments of the Aetherial rulers, the Circle of Five<br></li><li>armor of the beast god, Mogdrogen</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701090/extras/DLC_Loyalist03_Banner_Empyrion01.jpg?t=1709053495\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701090/extras/DLC_Loyalist03_Bitmap_Empyrion01.gif?t=1709053495\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams